To help with your navigation of the area, the Student Resource Center has complied a list of banks, supermarkets, stores, and other businesses that are within the vicinity of NYU's campus.                                                           STORAGE and MOVING                               We are often asked whether it is better to store belongings over the summer in New York or to mail or drive them home. The answer is, it depends on your individual circumstances: the distance home, the amount of material to be moved, whether you prefer to spend money or time, whether your student will need access to belongings over the summer, and other factors.    Lightly-used boxes can often be obtained for free or at low cost from local stores or by searching craigslist.org.    Residence Halls will often collect unwanted electronics, clothes, home goods, food, and other items to be recycled or donated at the end of the year. Students should check with their building's Resource Center for more details.    Also note that students should check with their Residence Hall staff for information about local parking, best hours for check out, and short extensions of their move-out date (if necessary).   Many of the following companies provide discount or special rates for students and usually require proof of enrollment such as a student ID or use of an NYU email address.   Stop&Stor  10% student discount available for students, must have their NYU ID.  Call: 718.996.8000.     Collegiate Storage and Rental  Rentals of refrigerators, microwaves, as well as shipping, storage, and packing supplies. Call for discount rates.  Call: 718.267.6484   Flat Rate - MOVEU  Call for discount information: 212.988.9292.     Tuck-it-Away  Call: 866-549-4740 or Sales@tuckitaway.com     Box Butler  10% discount with valid ID or NYU e-mail  Provide containers of various sizes, price includes pick-up and delivery. Call 888.881.0810 or check their website for details.     Keepers  25% student discount on 5x5 storage space.  Call: 212.674.2176 for information and reservations.     Collegeboxes  Shipping, pick-up, storage, and delivery.  Call: 866.BOX.ITUP (866.269.4887) for discount info during the year.     dorm2dorm.com  Supplies, pick-up, storage, and delivery.  Call: 646.476.5763 - call for discount info.   Manhattan Mini Storage  Offers student discounts.  For student rates call 212.Storage (786.7243).   OZ Moving  Offers a 10% discount for NYU students.  Call: 212.452.6683     Chelsea Mini-Storage  Offers discounts for students and curbside pickup. For details, inquiries, and reservations call 212.564.7735 or 877.902.9751   Storage Post Self Storage  Special rates are available Call: 1.888.370.0088 for details.
